HEADWORD: Transhuman
<hw>Trans*hu"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>trans-</ets> + <ets>human</ets>.]</ety> <def>More than human;
superhuman.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Words may not tell of that <qex>transhuman</qex> change.</q>
<rj><qau>H. F. Cary.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transhumanize</ent>⟦br⟧
